## Description

Renders an .Rd file to an mdx file.






## Usage

```r
render_reference(rd_file, output_file, config_file = "_starlightr.toml")
```

## Arguments

<div class="arg-table">
<table>
<thead>
<tr><th>Argument</th><th>Description</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>rd_file</code></td>
<td>path to Rd file to convert to .mdx</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>output_file</code></td>
<td>path to new mdx file</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>config_file</code></td>
<td>path to _starlightr.toml</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>



## Examples

```r
# Not run:
render_reference(
  rd_file = "man/function.Rd",
  output_file = "../Docs/src/content/docs/reference/function.mdx",
  config_file = "_starlightr.toml"
)
```
